<h2>Idea</h2>
<p>The BIG idea is that we not only search the rooms but also use algorithms to RANK the results.</p>
<p>Two major parameters that Book!t takes into consideration are:
<p style="font-weight:bold">
    1. The distance between YOU and available rooms;</p>
<p style="font-weight:bold">
    2. The difference between ATTENDEE# and CAPACITY of the room;
</p>

<h3>Approach</h3>
<p>
To bring this idea into reality we input all cubicles/cubicle islands/gateways/meeting rooms information (map nodes) and their relationships (map edges) into the database. 
</p>
